metadata.name: #1 Minimal life
metadata.description:
#1

The debut collection, "Minimal life" consists of 100 unique NFTs. 
This project began on December 17, 2021.

Less is more!
Finally, get rid of the ballast! 
Minimalism makes you happy - and it can be so simple!
Minimalism means getting rid of unnecessary things or habits that are not good for you.

Is that what you expect from life?

Dimensions: 8248x8248 pixels
Collection: Minimal life
